          "trait": "Translated",
          "trait_date": "2026-05-07T15:10:00.3683291Z",
          "locale_text": "«Si se rompe usted mismo, no pienso arreglarlo»."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "locale": "trTR",
      "text": "\"Kendini bozarsan seni tamir etmem.\"",
